               <p>SAMUEL WHATMORE. I live in <placeName id="t18311201-181-crimeloc966">Drummond-crescent</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18311201-181-crimeloc966" type="placeName" value="Drummond-crescent"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18311201-181-crimeloc966" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-181-off964 t18311201-181-crimeloc966"></join>. The prisoner came to my house to nurse my wife - she had been there about ten days, when I missed a sheet -I asked where it was; she said it was at the mangle, that the mangling woman had gone out to tea, and she could not have it that day.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311201-181-person1469">
