            . I am a pawnbroker, at Somers'-town. I have a child's gown, napkin, and shift, pawned by the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311201-181-person1470">
                  JOHN 
                  CALLER
               <interp inst="t18311201-181-person1470" type="surname" value="CALLER"></interp>
